</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCB369A49190D25FCF3B8A3FF41FE93" blockId="5.[801,1452,1719,1903]" lastBlockId="6.[136,787,279,335]" lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="47" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">
<emphasis id="B900EA8849190D26FCF3B8A3FCE0F912" box="[839,894,1720,1743]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Notes</emphasis>
. – 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D1949190D26FC29B8A3FBAFF912" box="[925,1073,1719,1743]" class="Jungermanniopsida" family="Lejeuneaceae" genus="Lejeunea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Porellales" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" phylum="Marchantiophyta" rank="species" species="flava">
<emphasis id="B900EA8849190D26FC29B8A3FBAFF912" box="[925,1073,1719,1743]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Lejeunea flava</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is widely distributed in tropical and warm-temperate regions of the world and distinguished by ovate-oblong leaves with rounded tips, leaf cells with conspicuous trigones, ± longer than wide underleaves with a cordate base, and gynoecia frequently two in a row on short branches (e.g., 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE54B6B49190D26FCEFB94CFB92F8B2" author="SCHUSTER, R. M." box="[859,1036,1879,1903]" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" refId="ref9159" refString="SCHUSTER, R. M. (1980). The Hepaticae and Anthocerotae of North America IV. Columbia University Press, New York." type="book" year="1980">SCHUSTER, 1980</bibRefCitation>
). Stephani’s description of 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D1949190D25FA9FB94CFF72FEF2" class="Jungermanniopsida" family="Lejeuneaceae" genus="Taxilejeunea" kingdom="Plantae" lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="47" order="Porellales" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" phylum="Marchantiophyta" rank="species" species="tenuiplica">
<emphasis id="B900EA8849190D25FA9FB94CFF72FEF2" italics="true" lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="47" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Taxilejeunea tenuiplica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
adds another name to the long list of synonyms of 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D19491A0D25FF3CBF23FF47FE92" box="[136,217,311,335]" class="Jungermanniopsida" family="Lejeuneaceae" genus="Lejeunea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Porellales" pageId="6" pageNumber="47" phylum="Marchantiophyta" rank="species" species="flava">
<emphasis id="B900EA88491A0D25FF3CBF23FF47FE92" box="[136,217,311,335]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">L. flava</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
